---
import { siteInfo, pages } from '@data/site.json';
import Icon from 'astro-icon';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-caramel-200/70">
      Thank you for considering EpoxyEdgeZZ for your epoxy table and furniture needs. We look
      forward to being a part of your journey to elevate your living spaces with timeless elegance.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-caramel-200/70">
      Follow us on <a
        href={siteInfo.socials.instagram}
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-orange-500 underline"
        ><Icon name="fa:instagram" class="inline h-4 w-4" /> Instagram</a
      > for the latest updates, inspiration, and behind-the-scenes glimpses of our creative process.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
